  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/2845b743a452563548d5dd344614f97e.avif?t=1744828738\" width=610 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chimp Memory is a logic puzzle and problem-solving game that challenges and teaches you about monkey research processes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to perform neurological tests similar to the ones they do, memorizing number sequences and matching the order of the numbers after they become invisible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/e95d3c218960eaa0f0d111c2093e3a57.poster.avif?t=1744828738\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/e95d3c218960eaa0f0d111c2093e3a57.webm?t=1744828738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/e95d3c218960eaa0f0d111c2093e3a57.mp4?t=1744828738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The tests are basically memory tests, in which the chimpanzees receive training and are great at what they do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your challenge is to perform better in the memory and logical reasoning test, like this:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/3dfdf6d864222be904a97cf8f54bc396.poster.avif?t=1744828738\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/3dfdf6d864222be904a97cf8f54bc396.webm?t=1744828738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your name in the Steam global ranking and prove that a simple monkey can't outsmart you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks and don't forget to add the game to your wishlist to support us! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/2845b743a452563548d5dd344614f97e.avif?t=1744828738\" width=610 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chimp Memory is a logic puzzle and problem-solving game that challenges and teaches you about monkey research processes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to perform neurological tests similar to the ones they do, memorizing number sequences and matching the order of the numbers after they become invisible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/e95d3c218960eaa0f0d111c2093e3a57.poster.avif?t=1744828738\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/e95d3c218960eaa0f0d111c2093e3a57.webm?t=1744828738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/e95d3c218960eaa0f0d111c2093e3a57.mp4?t=1744828738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The tests are basically memory tests, in which the chimpanzees receive training and are great at what they do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your challenge is to perform better in the memory and logical reasoning test, like this:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/3dfdf6d864222be904a97cf8f54bc396.poster.avif?t=1744828738\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036280/extras/3dfdf6d864222be904a97cf8f54bc396.webm?t=1744828738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your name in the Steam global ranking and prove that a simple monkey can't outsmart you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks and don't forget to add the game to your wishlist to support us! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
